44
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,000
You know him?

45
00:03:45,879 --> 00:03:47,400
He's a top student at the art academy.

46
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:49,879
He hasn't even graduated and he's already won many awards.

47
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:52,080
You're probably the only one who doesn't know him.

48
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:56,520
