83
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,519
Professor Zhong.

84
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,920
The one who taught us in college.

85
00:06:39,519 --> 00:06:40,399
Why do you want to see him?

86
00:06:41,879 --> 00:06:43,360
We're meeting Professor Zhong today.

87
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:45,040
We haven't seen him much since graduation.

88
00:06:45,199 --> 00:06:46,360
We set this up a few days ago.

89
00:06:53,199 --> 00:06:54,839
