107
00:08:15,759 --> 00:08:16,160
Xiao Lu.

108
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:16,800
We arranged this a few days ago.

109
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:18,240
The one who taught us in college.

110
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,279
Why do you want to see him?

111
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,200
Who are you looking for?

112
00:09:03,919 --> 00:09:05,720
Excuse me, is Professor Zhong home?

113
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,000
