116
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,679
I've lived here for five years.

117
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:29,919
Hello.

118
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,720
Do you know where Yuan You is?

119
00:09:35,919 --> 00:09:36,600
He's over there.

120
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,320
Xiao Tangyuan.

121
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,320
Are you drawing?

122
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:01,759
Looks like you really do come here often.

123
00:10:08,879 --> 00:10:10,080
So should we...

124
00:10:11,679 --> 00:10:13,159
talk about what happened that night?

125
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:18,519
So who was that man that night?

126
00:10:19,039 --> 00:10:20,679
Why did he do that to you?

127
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:26,919
It's none of your business.

128
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:31,840
Then what do you want to talk to me about?

129
00:11:01,879 --> 00:11:02,799
Xiao Tangyuan

130
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:05,279
Why did you draw this?

131
00:11:06,559 --> 00:11:07,759
Did you see something?

132
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:48,960
Xu Xin

133
00:11:57,519 --> 00:11:58,519
Why are you here?

134
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:00,320
I came to take you home.

135
00:12:01,399 --> 00:12:02,720
How did you know I was here?

136
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:03,840
