144
00:12:24,279 --> 00:12:25,600
This was before the accident.

145
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:27,240
You might not remember.

146
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,039
I don't remember.

147
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,919
But I think

148
00:12:37,759 --> 00:12:39,639
I wouldn't have let you install something like that.

149
00:12:42,519 --> 00:12:43,840
I don't want this.

150
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:45,159
Please uninstall it for me.

151
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:45,799
Xu Xin

152
00:12:45,919 --> 00:12:47,039
Please uninstall it right now.

153
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:47,840
What's wrong?

154
00:12:54,919 --> 00:12:55,639
I remember you.

155
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:59,440
We met at the psychology clinic, right?

156
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:05,240
Xu Xin

157
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:07,600
Is this your friend?

158
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:12,519
My name is Yuan You.

159
00:13:13,279 --> 00:13:14,480
She often comes here to see the kids.

160
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:15,919
That's why I recognize her.

161
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:23,440
Xu Xin

162
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:26,919
Let's go home.

163
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:18,679
Don't go to that welfare home anymore.

164
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:26,000
Lu Ming, you just don't understand.

165
00:14:26,639 --> 00:14:28,120
I can't explain it to you.

166
00:14:28,120 --> 00:14:29,799
I really saw someone get killed.

167
00:14:30,919 --> 00:14:31,919
It's all in your imagination.

168
00:14:32,159 --> 00:14:34,320
No, this isn't a hallucination.

169
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:36,039
Xiao Tangyuan's drawing.

170
00:14:36,039 --> 00:14:36,759
Xu Xin.

171
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:46,000
Stop using your fantasies as an excuse.

172
00:14:49,320 --> 00:14:51,080
Don't think I don't know you went to the welfare home.

173
00:14:51,799 --> 00:14:52,840
I know what you're really doing there.

174
00:14:58,759 --> 00:14:59,799
What are you talking about?

175
00:15:07,799 --> 00:15:08,840
That male caregiver.

176
00:15:10,080 --> 00:15:11,559
When he stands next to you,

177
00:15:14,159 --> 00:15:15,080
I feel like an outsider.

178
00:15:25,639 --> 00:15:26,279
Lu Ming.

179
00:15:29,039 --> 00:15:30,159
Why would you think that?

180
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:34,679
Let's eat.

181
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:38,679
I can't eat anymore.

182
00:15:58,559 --> 00:15:59,519
Then don't eat.

183
00:16:01,519 --> 00:16:02,360
From now on,

184
00:16:03,399 --> 00:16:04,639
don't go to the welfare home anymore.

185
00:17:48,640 --> 00:17:49,200
Hello.

186
00:17:49,319 --> 00:17:51,440
I'm Lin Qing, a reporter from Art Digest.

187
00:17:51,599 --> 00:17:52,880
You're Lu Ming's wife.

188
00:17:54,839 --> 00:17:56,440
My husband isn't home today.

189
00:17:56,759 --> 00:17:58,279
Maybe you could come another day.

190
00:17:58,799 --> 00:17:59,759
I'm not here for him.

191
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:01,160
I'm here specifically to see you.

192
00:18:02,759 --> 00:18:03,599
Reporter Lin.

193
00:18:04,440 --> 00:18:05,119
Please have some tea.

194
00:18:05,359 --> 00:18:07,680
Thank you. Just call me Lin Qing.

195
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:09,319
I'll start recording now.

196
00:18:14,359 --> 00:18:15,799
My husband isn't home.

197
00:18:17,160 --> 00:18:20,279
I'm not sure what I can say.

198
00:18:22,200 --> 00:18:24,160
Actually, this is my first time talking to a reporter.

199
00:18:24,440 --> 00:18:26,000
It's okay, don't be so nervous.

200
00:18:26,119 --> 00:18:27,359
Let's just have a casual chat.

201
00:18:28,079 --> 00:18:31,000
At your husband's recent exhibition closing,

202
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,480
I heard you were supposed to attend.

203
00:18:32,839 --> 00:18:34,079
But you weren't feeling well,

204
00:18:34,079 --> 00:18:35,480
so you couldn't make it, right?

205
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:41,000
I was in a car accident not long ago.

206
00:18:42,680 --> 00:18:46,079
So my memory is still a bit confused.

207
00:18:47,279 --> 00:18:50,279
And I'm afraid going out would trouble him.

208
00:18:51,279 --> 00:18:52,720
You mentioned confusion.

209
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:55,079
Does that mean between you two,

210
00:18:55,079 --> 00:18:56,960
