00:24:53,119 --> 00:24:54,519
I've always thought

285
00:24:54,599 --> 00:24:56,759
you would achieve great things in the future.

286
00:24:57,359 --> 00:24:58,680
And I was right.

287
00:24:59,000 --> 00:25:00,960
Now you're already a renowned artist.

288
00:25:01,680 --> 00:25:04,480
And you still respect your teachers so much.

289
00:25:04,599 --> 00:25:05,640
You even came to visit me.

290
00:25:06,839 --> 00:25:07,839
Thank you both.

291
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:10,799
You're too kind, Professor Zhong.

292
00:25:13,039 --> 00:25:13,920
Professor Zhong,

293
00:25:15,599 --> 00:25:18,799
I didn't expect you'd changed so much.

294
00:25:19,759 --> 00:25:21,200
Well, I've gotten old.

295
00:25:21,440 --> 00:25:23,440
No one can escape the passage of time.

296
00:25:24,200 --> 00:25:25,119
But I'm doing fine.

297
00:25:25,400 --> 00:25:28,400
I still have these old friends to keep me company.

298
00:25:30,519 --> 00:25:33,519
Xu Xin, I remember you as well.

299
00:25:33,839 --> 00:25:35,119
You attended quite a few of my classes too.

300
00:25:37,240 --> 00:25:40,799
Professor Zhong, may I ask you something?

301
00:25:41,680 --> 00:25:43,000
Where is your wife?

302
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:52,680
I'm all alone.

303
00:25:53,599 --> 00:25:56,640
In the end, I chose not to get married.

304
00:25:57,400 --> 00:26:00,279
I think being alone is just fine.

305
00:26:01,519 --> 00:26:02,160
But...

306
00:26:04,599 --> 00:26:08,799
I heard you married a much younger woman.

307
00:26:12,599 --> 00:26:13,359
Her name is...

308
00:26:14,880 --> 00:26:15,799
Xiao Ya.

309
00:26:17,680 --> 00:26:19,519
You must have heard wrong.

310
00:26:23,240 --> 00:26:23,920
Lu Ming,

311
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:26,880
Seeing you and Xu Xin so happy now,

312
00:26:27,039 --> 00:26:28,240
I'm truly happy for you.

313
00:26:29,119 --> 00:26:31,920
I think your relationship is as solid as a rock,

314
00:26:32,079 --> 00:26:33,440
and will last a thousand years.

315
00:26:36,759 --> 00:26:37,720
Thank you, Professor Zhong.

316
00:26:38,559 --> 00:26:40,160
Seeing how carefree you are now,

317
00:26:40,960 --> 00:26:42,200
I'm happy for you too.

318
00:26:42,960 --> 00:26:45,400
It seems those things from back then

319
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:47,400
no longer affect you.

320
00:26:51,599 --> 00:26:52,640
What things?

321
00:26:53,799 --> 00:26:55,759
The past is best left unspoken.

322
00:26:55,839 --> 00:26:56,599
Professor Zhong,

323
00:26:57,480 --> 00:26:58,960
I actually think that incident

324
00:26:59,519 --> 00:27:00,640
must have had more to it.

325
00:27:02,039 --> 00:27:03,880
A teacher as principled as you,

326
00:27:04,319 --> 00:27:05,519
how could you possibly have

327
00:27:05,519 --> 00:27:06,960
an improper relationship with a female student?

328
00:27:08,880 --> 00:27:12,839
Back then, a female student pursued me.

329
00:27:13,119 --> 00:27:14,160
I refused her.

330
00:27:14,920 --> 00:27:17,599
But then she turned it around on me.

331
00:27:17,680 --> 00:27:19,519
She told the school I was the one pursuing her.

332
00:27:20,119 --> 00:27:21,279
Just that trivial matter.

333
00:27:22,359 --> 00:27:24,240
The school really didn't get the facts straight.

334
00:27:24,519 --> 00:27:26,079
It was clearly the girl's fault.

335
00:27:26,720 --> 00:27:28,119
Why were you the one punished?

336
00:27:29,640 --> 00:27:31,119
Can we not talk about this anymore?

337
00:27:34,880 --> 00:27:35,920
Sorry, Professor Zhong.

338
00:27:37,039 --> 00:27:38,319
It's just so nice to see you.

339
00:27:38,799 --> 00:27:39,759
I spoke too much.

340
00:27:40,480 --> 00:27:41,200
Please forgive me.

341
00:27:45,720 --> 00:27:46,960
Yes, I should be more forgiving.

342
00:27:47,359 --> 00:27:50,440
Young people today really do respect their teachers.

343
00:27:50,839 --> 00:27:52,839
You came to see me, but brought nothing.

344
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:55,839
We actually wanted to bring a gift.

345
00:27:56,240 --> 00:27:57,200
But we were in a rush.

346
00:27:58,880 --> 00:28:01,480
Professor Zhong, how about this—

347
00:28:02,519 --> 00:28:05,160
Let me transfer you some money as a token of thanks.

348
00:28:05,799 --> 00:28:06,839
What are you saying?

349
00:28:07,240 --> 00:28:07,799
Lu Ming,

350
00:28:10,519 --> 00:28:11,279
Do you want to...

351
00:28:41,400 --> 00:28:42,079
I really don't understand

352
00:28:42,079 --> 00:28:43,279
why you want to find this person.

353
00:28:44,599 --> 00:28:45,880
And about Xiaoya you just mentioned,

354
00:28:46,000 --> 00:28:47,319
what exactly happened with that?

355
00:28:49,359 --> 00:28:51,599
How about we go see Dr. Xu?

356
00:28:51,599 --> 00:28:53,079
You don't understand anything at all.

357
00:28:54,799 --> 00:28:55,440
What's wrong?

358
00:29:01,160 --> 00:29:02,200
You should go home first.

359
00:29:03,240 --> 00:29:04,599
I want to walk alone for a while.

360
00:29:06,039 --> 00:29:06,839
I can go with you.

361
00:29:07,119 --> 00:29:07,759
No need.

362
00:29:08,920 --> 00:29:10,359
I just need some time alone.

363
00:29:15,039 --> 00:29:15,599
Okay.

364
00:29:44,559 --> 00:29:45,880
Do you still remember Professor Zhong?

365
00:29:47,240 --> 00:29:48,160
Why bring him up?

366
00:29:49,599 --> 00:29:50,720
Today,

367
00:29:52,319 --> 00:29:53,400
I met him.

368
00:29:56,000 --> 00:29:57,119
How is he doing?

369
00:29:57,839 --> 00:29:58,559
Not well.

370
00:30:00,039 --> 00:30:01,200
Because of misconduct.

371
00:30:02,480 --> 00:30:03,319
How do you know?

372
00:30:05,799 --> 00:30:07,759
I've known for a long time that he's not a good person.

373
00:30:08,519 --> 00:30:10,559
I heard about it when I first started college.

374
00:30:10,559 --> 00:30:11,799
He pursued one of our senior classmates.

375
00:30:12,960 --> 00:30:15,720
It's said that he even harassed someone.

376
00:30:16,039 --> 00:30:17,400
It just wasn't exposed.

377
00:30:19,400 --> 00:30:21,200
Back then, I really couldn't tell.

378
00:30:22,799 --> 00:30:25,319
Xu Xin, you're too kind.

379
00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:27,000
The world is dangerous.

380
00:30:27,240 --> 00:30:29,039
You must be cautious of everyone around you.

381
00:31:01,440 --> 00:31:02,880
I might really be sick.
